data.description: Come live in the beautiful community of Bella Vista! This home sits on a huge corner lot without any neighbors behind. It has an open floor plan, spacious bedrooms with walk-in closets and a second floor living space. This home is complete with a refrigerator and washer/dryer included. The large backyard has a huge deck with plenty of room for a playscape and room to run. The Bella Vista community has a great common area with a pool and play area.
